snippet.title: Hell Let Loose - Devotion to Duty Update Announcement | PC Gaming Show 2023
snippet.description:
Announced during the PC Gaming Show 2023, historical multiplayer FPS Hell Let Loose shares the Objective mode in its Devotion to Duty update. This shorter and faster game mode will feature smaller teams of just 25 players. Take a look at the new Brécourt Manor Assault map. Read more on PC Gamer: https://www.pcgamer.com/hell-let-loose-objective-mode-reveal-pcgs-2023
